---
title: Cal Smart Roasted Double Salmon with Veggie Bulgur and Lemon Aioli
description: This light, bright meal of seasoned salmon fillets is simplicity at its best! It's finished with a dollop of lemon aioli and served on a bed of savoury roasted zucchini and peppers tossed with bulgur.

